OL,3,CDramatic decline in insect populations
OL,4,Cover last 50 years, study finds
OL,6,FA survey of farmland in Sussex,
OL,7,Fcarried out for more than 50 years,
OL,8,Fhas seen a dramatic decline in insect
OL,9,Fpopulations.
OL,11,FThe study tests the number of
OL,12,Fdifferent insects present on cereal
OL,13,Fcrops which overall has revealed that
OL,14,Fnumbers have dropped by 37%.
OL,16,FIt is done by using a vacuum backpack
OL,17,Fto sample the insects living amongst
OL,18,Fthe cereal.
