OL,3,CDramatic decline in insect populations
OL,4,Cover last 50 years, study finds
OL,6,FJulie Ewald from the Game and Wildlife
OL,7,FConservation Trust said: "We do not
OL,8,Fthink that this is the farmers' fault.
OL,10,F"We think this is a combination of
OL,11,Fwhat society wants, which is cheap
OL,12,Ffood, and also the way that government
OL,13,Fhas pushed farmers into becoming more
OL,14,Fintensive.
OL,16,F"British farmers are very aware of
OL,17,Ftheir environmental footprint and are
OL,18,Fwanting to do the right things for
OL,19,Fwildlife"
